# .aidocs/index.aidocs - Documentation Index

This file routes to the shared documentation that applies across projects.

Router policy: this file is a link/list router only. Do not treat it as a forced full-load import list.

## Shared Docs
- `.aidocs/global-instructions.aidocs`
- `.aidocs/coding-standards.aidocs`
- `.aidocs/memory-system.aidocs`
- `.aidocs/research-safety.aidocs`
- `.aidocs/project-init.aidocs`
- `.aidocs/project-update.aidocs`
- `.aidocs/personality-system.aidocs`
- `.aidocs/reingest-system.aidocs`
- `.aidocs/cleanup-system.aidocs`

## Project-Specific Docs
Each project should add its own documentation index and link it here as it is created.
Use `/project-init` to initialize a new project.
Use `/project-update` to sync system files in already initialized projects.
